{"tid":1300600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不滿佔中堵路致業務受損 投資公司事隔五年入禀向佔中九子索償","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:56:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T12:26:29.000Z","uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"78319329fc7d281bd36d2034cc7ef26cd7619688","tid":1300600,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"2014年佔領運動持續79天後落幕。事隔將近5年，有投資公司不滿當年的道路堵塞導致中港業務受損，自言慘成受害人，今年以苦主身份入稟小額錢債審裁處，向被判公眾妨擾等罪名成立的佔中九子索償4.5萬元。案件定於明早10時在西九龍法院大樓作簡短提訊，有關樓層今早張貼通告及架設臨時欄杆，表明公眾及傳媒需以先到先得方式輪候籌號，才可入庭旁聽。<br />\n<br />\n申索人偉俊策略投資有限公司，是上市公司偉俊集團控股（1013）的全資附屬公司，報稱地址在金鐘夏愨道海富中心。被告依序為陳淑莊、邵家臻、戴耀廷、李永達、黃浩銘、陳健民、張秀賢、鍾耀華、朱耀明，申索書上鍾耀華的<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「華」字寫成簡體字「华」</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">班員工係咪想早d收工？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c678b22490e09602059a2913632875c03146d4f","tid":1300600,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"301b514a8f85c0984f6a105c84bd7f712d681307","tid":1300600,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:57:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fd6a9c0b49bc3f667c63053282fc865c8c19cfa","tid":1300600,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:57:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdd789062b92c1d25f1911872d92ec0907fd0f8f","tid":1300600,"uid":80356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2df831e5cae